            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Fortunae <lb n="2"/>Respicienti <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Nasellius Pro<lb break="no" n="4"/>clianus |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> prae<lb break="no" n="6"/>positus c<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>hor</abbr><ex>tis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>I Helvetiorum <lb n="8"/>Torquato et <lb n="9"/>Iuliano <lb n="10"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der Vorderseite der corona eine Mondsichel. (B): Haug - Sixt; Filtzinger; Fabricius - Hettner - Sarwey: Z. 2: sac(rum); Schmidt Heidenreich: Fehlender ZeilenfallZ. 8/9; Z. 10 fehlt. Aufbewahrungsort des Originals unbekannt. Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
